This project explores Walmart sales data through SQL queries to extract meaningful business insights. Key areas of analysis include:

Overall and category-wise sales performance
Monthly and weekday trends
Customer behavior by branch and payment method
Product line performance

The dataset includes transactional details such as invoice ID, branch, customer type, product line, total amount, and timestamps.

ðŸ“Œ Tools Used:

MySQL
Public Walmart sales dataset (CSV)


This beginner-friendly project helps understand how SQL can be used to analyze and summarize large retail datasets efficiently.
